{"tid":117602,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《矛盾戰爭》正式開拍 改名為《明日戰紀》 劉青雲古天樂主演","createTime":"2017-02-12T10:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T14:28:05.000Z","uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58bdc9d5569402537fb7b45183e61cdcb84c2f7","tid":117602,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:53:24.000Z","msg":"轉貼至mtime<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mtime.com/2017/02/12/1566288.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mtime.com%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F1566288.html&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=562afbc5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mtime.com/2017/02/12/1566288.html</a><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;時光網訊&nbsp;正月剛過，勞模古天樂和劉青雲又開工啦！這回他倆要一起合作一部科幻大片《明日戰記》，該片已於今日在深圳正式開機拍攝。從片場照看來，除了古、劉主演之外，演技派姜皓文、憑《點五步》提名金像獎最佳新人獎的鬍子彤和《我是路人甲》男主角萬國鵬都參演了該片。<br />\n<br />\n《明日戰記》就是古天樂作為幕後&ldquo;大BOSS&rdquo;籌備多年的科幻電影《矛盾戰爭》，這些年有關影片的導演人選也一直在發生著變化，從早前的陳木勝、羅志良到如今的吳炫輝（高輝），吳炫輝長於視覺特效，《風雲2》《畫皮》《投名狀》《太極1》都是他的視覺特效代表作。<br />\n<br />\n影片去年底在廣電總局備案立項，由羅志良擔任編劇，講述了在地球環境惡化，冰川融化，糧食能源短缺，全球經濟崩潰，人造衛星缺乏資金維修，通訊科技退回到70年代的大背景下，神秘的機械人從水底登岸，襲擊世界各個城市，為了保護人類，全球各大國組成&ldquo;國際和平聯盟&rdquo;，對抗機械人的故事。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《明日戰記》由大陸的引力傳媒和古天樂自己的天下一電影公司共同投資製作。眾所周知，古天樂是個科幻大片愛好者，尤其迷戀超級英雄電影，私藏1:1手辦無數。 《矛盾戰爭》是他一直想拍攝的科幻大片，他此前也收購了許多後期製作、數碼特效和特效化妝的公司。 《明日戰記》的主要特效便會由古天樂的特效公司製作，他早前曾表示，希望通過這部大片證明香港的特效已達國際水平。該片預計2018年上映。<br />\n<br />\n編輯：歐子"},{"pid":"d67e04fbc969e73654bef76a965d8d30ff8bd45f","tid":117602,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"古天樂同劉青雲係咪組合？"},{"pid":"b4d63b1c0dedb385ab666a06868265f872d3deaa","tid":117602,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"大陸片......"},{"pid":"cda6b26d5cf5ccf374c8c01c4b42ee559bfc8af5","tid":117602,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然實有人屌 估唔到搵埋劉青雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847f16dc81ff39ad6b629a53d887a111cf8f340e","tid":117602,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac64c98155c3bb34cea2e34fcf9d20066969b99f","tid":117602,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"原來由陳木勝變左吳炫輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6fe7aedf366ab7f7df32edb7ed260b611e708e","tid":117602,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"又係佢地"},{"pid":"448489b338c9e3894c035badd2785ae68dee8299","tid":117602,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"簡轉繁直出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬍子彤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff81dc51229f256f1ea6aa1766ce37759ba4c0e","tid":117602,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"又有黑仔"},{"pid":"786b210f48af79a4de1e66dd4efed85184d23000","tid":117602,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡轉繁直出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬍子彤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n將就下啦 香港比較少電影網站咁詳細報電影料"},{"pid":"0297894f0e117edfdf04f5f924683e9af63f8f4b","tid":117602,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來由陳木勝變左吳炫輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁拍到全城戒備咁好難令人有信心既"}